        "content": "# Device Telemetry\nReusable dashboard for Moqui devices.\n\n- `ParameterLog`: numeric series and latest parameter values.\n- `Measurement`: one time series per measurement type and scope.\n- `DeviceLog`: chronological payload stream.\n\nCurrent device: `${device_id}`",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.0.0",
      "title": "Overview",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "postgres",
        "uid": "moqui-postgres"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
